ShittyItem_MaxNumberToSpawn_MedkitToolbo.Description: The maximum number of toolbox/flashlight/medkit to spawn

MinDiceRollToIncreaseMagicItemVariety.Description: The minimum dice roll value required to enforce that the magic item type (boot/bracer) that will be spawned in the chest will be different based on the current equipment of the player

MinDiceRollEnsuringNewItemOrSpellCounter.Description: The minimum dice roll value required to enforce that the magic item counter (Fly/FOTD/MageHand/Dispelling) that will be spawned in the chest will be different based on the current equipment of the player
